I"<<p>This evening’s main topic was ‘Sports Photography’.</p>

<p>An extensive topic that requires a knowledge of the sport being photographed incorporating the need to show movement within the activity. A slideshow was shown providing several aspects of the genre, including team and individual sporting activities. </p>

<p><br /></p>

<hr />

<p><br /></p>

<p>The ‘Monthly Competition’ entitled ‘Broken Glass’ was held.</p>

<p>The winners were:-</p>

<ul>
	<li>1st - 'Bits &amp; Pieces' by Linda Evans</li>
	<li>2nd - 'No Need To Wash' by John Horton</li>
	<li>3rd - 'Vandalism' by Joan Banks</li>
</ul>

